<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/cursor') %>
  <%- include('partials/nav') %>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="cc-hero">
    <div class="cc-hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="cc-hero-content">
      <span class="cs-hero-eyebrow">Crew Call</span>
      <h1 class="cs-hero-title">Tedrad</h1>
      <p class="cs-hero-sub">Steps Through Time — Narrative Short Film</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Project Summary -->
  <section class="cs-content">
    <div class="cs-content-inner reveal">
      <div class="cs-content-left">
        <span class="cs-content-eyebrow">Overview</span>
        <h2 class="cs-content-heading">Project<br>Summary</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-content-right">
        <p><strong>Tedrad: Steps Through Time</strong> is a high-concept narrative short that deconstructs the architecture of grief across four distinct visual chapters: Trapped, Escape, Reckoning, and Release.</p>
        <p>Following the success of our previous production — which reached nearly 100,000 impressions in its debut month — this project leverages a proven distribution model and a strategic cross-channel collaboration.</p>
        <p>We are seeking a dedicated crew to help elevate this visual poem for a global digital audience.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Narrative -->
  <section class="cc-narrative">
    <div class="cc-narrative-inner reveal">
      <span class="cs-content-eyebrow" style="color: rgba(240,237,232,0.4);">The Narrative</span>
      <h2 class="cs-content-heading" style="color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 40px;">The Story</h2>
      <p>The film follows Nico through a series of repeating cycles and transformations. From a surreal, looping beach to the sensory overload of a city party, Tedrad uses evocative locations and a licensed soundtrack by NF ("Hope" & "Time") to explore how we move through loss.</p>
      <p>This is a visual-first production with a focus on rhythmic editing and distinct color palettes for each chapter.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Roles Available -->
  <section class="cc-roles">
    <div class="cc-roles-inner">
      <div class="cc-roles-header reveal">
        <span class="cs-content-eyebrow" style="color: rgba(240,237,232,0.4);">Open Positions</span>
        <h2 class="cs-content-heading" style="color: var(--white);">Roles<br>Available</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="cc-roles-grid">
        <div class="cc-role-card reveal">
          <h3 class="cc-role-title">Director of Photography</h3>
          <p class="cc-role-desc">To lead the visual identity of four unique environments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cc-role-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <h3 class="cc-role-title">Sound Recordist / Mixer</h3>
          <p class="cc-role-desc">Crucial for capturing environmental textures and atmospheric soundscapes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cc-role-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <h3 class="cc-role-title">Gaffer / Lighting Tech</h3>
          <p class="cc-role-desc">To manage the transition from "warm memory" to "cold reality."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cc-role-card reveal">
          <h3 class="cc-role-title">Production Designer</h3>
          <p class="cc-role-desc">To oversee the symbolic continuity of the four stages.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cc-role-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <h3 class="cc-role-title">Editor / Colorist</h3>
          <p class="cc-role-desc">Experience with non-linear, music-driven narratives preferred.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="cc-roles-header reveal" style="margin-top: 60px;">
        <span class="cs-content-eyebrow" style="color: rgba(240,237,232,0.4);">Casting</span>
        <h2 class="cs-content-heading" style="color: var(--white);">Roles<br>Available</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="cc-roles-grid">
        <div class="cc-role-card reveal">
          <h3 class="cc-role-title">Nico</h3>
          <p class="cc-role-desc">Young male, 21–30. The lead character navigating grief through repeating cycles and transformations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cc-role-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <h3 class="cc-role-title">Cora</h3>
          <p class="cc-role-desc">Young female, 21–30. A key presence in Nico's journey through loss and memory.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Compensation & Benefits -->
  <section class="cs-content">
    <div class="cs-content-inner reveal">
      <div class="cs-content-left">
        <span class="cs-content-eyebrow">What We Offer</span>
        <h2 class="cs-content-heading">Compensation<br>& Benefits</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-content-right">
        <div class="cc-benefit">
          <h4 class="cc-benefit-title">Expenses Covered</h4>
          <p>Full travel costs covered and professional catering/food provided on set.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cc-benefit">
          <h4 class="cc-benefit-title">Backend Equity</h4>
          <p>Key crew will receive a percentage-based share (Points) of the film's lifetime YouTube AdSense revenue.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cc-benefit">
          <h4 class="cc-benefit-title">Threshold Payouts</h4>
          <p>Dividends are issued monthly once an individual's accrued share reaches a &pound;100 threshold.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cc-benefit">
          <h4 class="cc-benefit-title">Portfolio Assets</h4>
          <p>High-resolution 4K/6K stills and clips provided for professional showreels.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cc-benefit">
          <h4 class="cc-benefit-title">Formal Agreement</h4>
          <p>A formal Memorandum of Understanding will be provided to all equity partners.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Apply -->
  <section class="cc-apply">
    <div class="cc-apply-inner reveal">
      <span class="cs-content-eyebrow" style="color: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);">Get Involved</span>
      <h2 class="cs-content-heading" style="color: var(--black); margin-bottom: 32px;">How to<br>Apply</h2>
      <p class="cc-apply-text">Send a link to your portfolio or reel and a brief note regarding your interest in the project.</p>
      <p class="cc-apply-text">Please use the subject line: <strong>"TEDRAD CREW — [Your Role]"</strong></p>
      <a href="mailto:<%= contactEmail %>?subject=TEDRAD%20CREW%20%E2%80%94%20[Your%20Role]" class="cc-apply-btn">Apply Now</a>
      <div class="cc-apply-details">
        <div class="cc-apply-detail">
          <span class="cc-apply-detail-label">Shoot Dates</span>
          <span class="cc-apply-detail-value">April — May</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cc-apply-detail">
          <span class="cc-apply-detail-label">Locations</span>
          <span class="cc-apply-detail-value">Ayrshire / Glasgow</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <%- include('partials/scripts') %>
</body>
</html>
